                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Powell</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Port au Prince</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-10-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 6, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Powell reports that the Provisional Government will, on October 7, issue
                    decree fixing date on which blockade is to become effective; that the Government
                    states it will, commencing October 10, place armed vessels at Gonaives and St.
                    Marc.)</p>
            </div>
